{
  "id": "6a0d47c23d726b0a9b5a4121",
  "title": "アイヌのウポポを聞いて目が覚めた",
  "created": 1779255235,
  "updated": 1779255240,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c23d726b0a9b5a4121",
      "text": "アイヌのウポポを聞いて目が覚めた",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255235
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf139",
      "text": "from [2026/05/20]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255235
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf13b",
      "text": "アイヌの歌と聞いて[. [2026/05/20#6a0d235f00000000004edc60]]、高3のコンクールで演奏した合唱の組曲[アイヌのウポポ]を思い出す[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255240
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf13c",
      "text": "\t[http://www.cam.hi-ho.ne.jp/kousaka/wagner/123rd/upopo.htm アイヌのウポポ]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf13d",
      "text": "\tほとんどのことは忘れてしまったが演奏にあたって、その言葉、文化、価値観を教えられたり、想像したり、話し合ったりしたなあ。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf13e",
      "text": "\t\tピリカは、小さいとか可愛いの意味だとこのとき初めて知ったり。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf13f",
      "text": "\t\tウポポは歌。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf140",
      "text": "\t夏休みなんかお盆以外毎日、曲を知り曲を練習しの繰り返し。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf141",
      "text": "\tクラシックの演奏、あるいは合唱に限らず表現というものは、対象に深く分け入る思考や作業なのだろう。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf142",
      "text": "\tどこかにうまい演奏がないか探してみよう。",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf143",
      "text": "\t[https://youtu.be/zGX9aMZPojY?si=CMX0ZNujShAYPBS9&t=802]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf144",
      "text": "\t\tうわーうまーすごー",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf145",
      "text": "\t\t眠かった目が覚めた",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255239
    },
    {
      "id": "6a0d47c300000000005cf146",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1779255235,
      "updated": 1779255235
    }
  ]
}